  "rationale": "<p>Choice B is correct. Substituting <i>x</i> = 0, 1, 2 into <i>y</i> = <i>x</i> &minus; 3 yields <i>y</i> = &minus;3, &minus;2, &minus;1, respectively.</p><p>The other tables match <i>y</i> = <i>x</i> + 3, <i>y</i> = &minus;<i>x</i> + 3, or <i>y</i> = <i>x</i>.</p>",
